A string containing the flags that users are allowed to adjust.
Include only the uppercase flag groupings here:
  A - controls set noack, ackall, ackimportant, ackstall, ackdeny, ackpost, ackreject
  C - controls set noeliminatecc, eliminatecc
  H - controls set nohide, hideaddress, hideall
  P - controls set noprefix, prefix
  R - controls set noreplyto, replyto
  S - controls set noselfcopy, selfcopy
  W - controls set norewritefrom, rewritefrom
If this is completely empty, users cannot adjust any of their flags.
The list owner can, of course, change anything using the list password.
A list of all possible flags is contained in "help set".

